name: Perfection
description: White is an inherently positive color, associated with purity, chastity, innocence, light, goodness, heaven, salvation, brilliance, illumination, understanding, cleanliness, faith, beginnings, spirituality, possibility, humility, sincerity, protection, tenderness, and  perfection.  but when it is stained with the slightest stain, does it invalidate that perfection?
